<p>如果不是悲伤难逃，</p> 
<p>谁愿彻夜泪流。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//26c1/26c145ef193a4b8578abe5e079c70446.com/large/1852000049e3969f7faa"></p> 
