<p>如果不是梦想还在，</p> 
<p>谁愿永不放手。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7145/7145b24a738e4559098b31b1fc995ff2.com/large/185100004a2b7e9188d8"></p> 
