<p>如果不是心有所牵，</p> 
<p>谁愿把泪当酒。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//d55b/d55b7133dc8df6789ea1b31e8bfb9c66.com/large/1852000049e5e00719cb"></p> 
